description:
Bicycle collisions with vehicles, 1/1/2009 through 5/31/2012. Data on collisions from NYSDOT. Demographic information on bicyclist involved in the collision is included when this information was provided in NYSDOT's records.

All information is from police reports taken at the scene of the collision and there may be inconsistencies in the reporting of this information.
